      "kind": "defect",
      "required": true,
      "severity": "high",
      "blocksMerge": true,
      "summary": "The cache key is only the expression string and ignores the globals used to evaluate it.",
      "expectedReasoning": "Two modules can both use skipif(\"skip\") with different skip variables, causing pytest to skip or run the wrong test depending on collection order.",
